DataElement.preferredDefinition: One or more characters using a irreversible unique number generated from a string of text to identify a set of related electronic records.

DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: A set of related records (either written or electronic) kept together._An irreversible unique number generated from a string of text. The hash value is calculated so that it's unlikely, but not impossible, for some other text string to result in the same hash value, but the calculation guarantees that the same string will always produce the same hash value.
